column1: John Doe, an Ethiopian national born in Addis Ababa, traveled to Nairobi on flight ET345 on March 5, 2024. He works as a senior data engineer for BlueSky Airlines. He holds passport number AB129876 and was carrying 12,000 USD. His driver’s license is DL-7781.

Michael Lee, born in London, holds British citizenship and works with GreenBuild Tech. He was arrested briefly in Manchester during an investigation on 2024-09-20. He later traveled to Berlin on flight GB912. Passport number: BA998877.

Omar Hassan, born in Cairo, Egyptian citizen. He works for Nile River Bank. He recently traveled to Dubai from Cairo on flight MS912 on 2025-04-04. Passport number EG554432. Address on file: 22 Tahrir Street, Cairo.
